    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's helpful. i really like the mill angle. what about the argument that the internet should basically be treated like a public square where the government has zero legitimacy to set any rules at all? i want to frame how even \"safety\" regulations are just a way for the state to control the narrative.",
